1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,260
大家早晨

2
00:00:01,260 --> 00:00:04,700
Good morning, everyone

3
00:00:04,700 --> 00:00:10,500
Let me say Happy Mother's Day

4
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:13,400
In addition to all the well wishes already

5
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:16,200
除了已經表達的祝福之外

6
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:18,200
讓我先說一聲母親節快樂

7
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:21,900
Very special that we can celebrate mums for all that they do

8
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:25,200
我們能夠一起慶祝母親節是非常特別

9
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:28,100
Mums are precious gifts from God

10
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,500
母親是神賜予的寶貴禮物

11
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,200
Let's face it, without them

12
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:35,500
family and home life would just fall apart

13
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:38,400
如果沒有了他們,家庭生活就會崩潰

14
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:43,200
Mums are so good at realizing and making sure that needs are met

15
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:46,800
媽媽們是非常擅長觀察家中的人

16
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,500
看看他們需要的是什麼

17
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:50,300
and that events can happen

18
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:52,300
為他們安排各種活動

19
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:55,200
and not just that they do it all themselves

20
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,000
他們為了自己

21
00:00:57,400 --> 00:01:00,000
but they know when others need to help out

22
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:03,200
而是知道其他人什麼時候需要他們的幫助

23
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:06,500
and organizing for these other people to make sure that things happen

24
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:08,400
他們就會為他們服務

25
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:11,600
Our passage of John 2, 1 to 12

26
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:14,400
shows us the brilliance of one particular mum

27
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:16,100
我們今天的經文

28
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:18,200
約翰福音二章一至十二節

29
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:20,600
向我們展示了一位特別的母親

30
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:23,900
and not that she makes herself the center of the story

31
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:28,600
but she sees a need and knows who to get involved

32
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:31,700
她並沒有將自己置於這個故事的中心

33
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:33,800
